The [platinum version at $3,700](https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings/design-your-own-ring/emerald-cut-diamond-three-stone-engagement-ring-with-pave-set-diamonds-in-platinum-by-james-allen-item-304297?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational) is the best choice here. Platinum is harder than gold and holds prong tips longer. For an emerald cut center — a shape with exposed corners — you want the hardest available metal holding those prongs in place.

