The Gallery Collection Vintage Trapezoid at [$24,800 setting price](https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings/design-your-own-ring/the-gallery-collection-vintage-three-stone-trapezoid-diamond-engagement-ring-14k-white-gold-item-203393?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational) is a significant setting investment — it includes substantial side stones already set in the ring. The center stone you add goes into an already complete ring frame. This is closer to a complete ring purchase than a "design your own" setting.

